comments.body: I zoomed it in and really can’t tell. Other than it’s not OCWA! I could believe NAWA.
I vote Nashville Warbler or Common Yellowthroat, but hard to see the bill in the photo.  The yellow seems bright and I think I see a good eye ring, so leaning Nashville.
